{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6e5bccc910","title":"新湖南报职工猛打穷追　又一右派集团现形","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ca670e5f06","index":0,"year":1957,"month":9,"day":11,"articleId":"6e5bccc910"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"06bbf56893","name":"新华社"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c7c1b2e068","type":"title","text":"新湖南报职工猛打穷追　又一右派集团现形","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e5bccc910"},{"id":"5157579fe7","type":"authors","text":"新华社","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e5bccc910"},{"id":"eb20a6140a","type":"paragraph","text":"据新华社讯:新湖南报社职工又揭发出一个右派小集团。这个右派小集团的成员有唐荫荪（民盟盟员、共青团员）、钟叔河（共青团员）、郑昌壬（共青团员）、朱纯（共青团员）和李长恭，都是新湖南报的编辑。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e5bccc910"},{"id":"201aa74ee3","type":"paragraph","text":"这个右派小集团极力为反党分子苏辛涛捧场，公开煽动新湖南报编辑部一些人提出要报社总编辑下台，请右派分子苏辛涛等人上台。他们还和社外的民盟右派集团密谋筹办一张在民盟右派领导下的并得到苏辛涛等同情和支持的反共反人民的“同人报”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e5bccc910"},{"id":"235946f2db","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《人民日报》1957年9月11日。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e5bccc910"}],"page":{"id":"27f5651ec1","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e5bccc910","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}